## Security Architecture

### Row-Level Security

```sql
-- Enable RLS on fact_revenue
ALTER TABLE fact_revenue ENABLE ROW LEVEL SECURITY;

-- Users can only see orgs they have access to
CREATE POLICY rls_revenue_org_access ON fact_revenue
    USING (org_id = ANY(get_user_accessible_orgs(current_setting('app.user_id')::UUID)));
```

### Roles

```sql
CREATE ROLE app_readonly;
GRANT SELECT ON ALL TABLES IN SCHEMA public TO app_readonly;
-- Revoke direct insert/update/delete from API layer
REVOKE INSERT, UPDATE, DELETE ON ALL TABLES IN SCHEMA public FROM app_readonly;
```

