## Technology Stack (Locked for Phase 1-2)

| Layer          | Technology          | Rationale                                |
|----------------|---------------------|------------------------------------------|
| Backend        | FastAPI (Python)    | Async, Pydantic validation, OpenAPI docs |
| Database       | PostgreSQL 15+      | JSONB, RLS, window functions, UUIDs      |
| ORM            | SQLAlchemy 2.0      | Async support, type safety               |
| Migrations     | Alembic             | Version-controlled schema changes        |
| Task Queue     | Celery + Redis      | Async ingestion pipelines                |
| Object Storage | MinIO / S3          | Raw file storage before ingestion        |
| MCP            | Python MCP SDK      | Anthropic-native protocol                |
| Caching        | Redis               | Query result caching                     |

